features: 💼【Durable Messenger Bag】 This messenger bag is made of durable, scratch-resistant and water resistant polyester fabric. Messenger bag for men equipped with smooth zipper and sturdy handle, plus the reinforced stitching at each stress point, make this laptop bag more durable for long-term use. Also, the briefcase has a front pocket which adopts leakproof zipper design can protect your belongings in rainy days.

💼【Roomy Organizer Briefcase】 The laptop briefcase is roomy to keep your items organized. There has 5 pockets on the outside of the bag. Under the cover, there also has 1 main padded pocket with a thick foam pad fits up to 15.6'' laptop. Also, it has multiple compartments to store books, document, folders and mouse. And has various separate pockets to store pen, business card or other small items. What's more, it has a detachable keychain can help you find your keys easily.

💼【Practical Satchel Bag】 This men briefcase has two anti-theft designs. There has a hidden pocket at the front of the satchel bag, the hidden zipper design is perfect for convenient and safe storage. The big zip pocket at the back of the messenger bag is safe for storage your important documents or your valuables. The computer bag also comes with a luggage strap to free your hands on the go.

💼【Laptop Bag Size】 The size of the messenger bag is 16.1" L * 5.1" W * 13" H, the detachable and removable shoulder strap length 33.9-55.9 inches, you could adjust length to meet your demand. Also, this satchel bag is designed with humanized cushioned handle and padded shoulder strap, which can better reduce your travel load and carry comfortably. It can be used as a messenger bag for work, business laptop bag, travel briefcase, crossbody shoulder bag, handbag and so on.

💼【Ideal Gift Choice】 This laptop briefcase features a classic and minimalist design, coupled with practical storage features, making it a professional messenger bag for men and women, suitable for matching and wearing on any occasions. The laptop tote bag is an ideal gift for mother, wife, sisters, yourself on Mother's Day, Valentine's Day, Christmas, birthdays, anniversaries or other holidays.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durable, perfect, my bag and me
reviews.reviewText: This is sooooo good. The straps are super high quality and it can hold so much stuff. I usually have my laptop, a folder, my notebook and my spiraled textbook, my two chargers, a pencil pouch, makeup, glasses AND my starbucks cup in the cup holder on the side and yeah its a little heavy (not as heavy as it would be if you used a totebag) BUT ITS AMAZINGGGGGGGIts so easy to grab ur stuff fr. Only rhing is that if ur plus size u might not be able to do it cross body just one arm.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice material, sturdy, great pockets
reviews.reviewText: I love this bag. It's huge but I need it to be. My one complaint is the design of the plastic carriers on the bag that receive the carabiner-type ends on the straps. The hole is not cut round, and the flat edge has corners. The strap end rubs on these corners and squeaks quite noticeably. It is 100% a design flaw, and annoys me, but I love everything else about this. Would give it 5 stars but for the squeak.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Looks Good But It Is To Squeaky
reviews.reviewText: The bag is really good, it looks amazing and it can withstand more harsher conditions. Even after raining, everything inside was protected. It has a laptop holder which is extremely useful. However it just makes so much noise that it's very annoying. I believe that it's because of the plastic handles that the bag makes lots squeaky noises which are awful. This can only be lessened by having lighter items in the bag or not having a ton in general. If you're going to carry a lot of stuff, it might be better to get another bag unfortunately.
